Female genitalia of 
<taxonomicName id="728B2AD8ED0AFF88FDADF8C8FB91F83E" authority="Yu, Maddison &amp; Zhang" authorityName="Yu, Maddison &amp; Zhang" authorityYear="2022" box="[574,1043,1918,1942]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Charippus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="24" pageNumber="175" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="heishiding" status="sp. nov.">
