Yu, Maddison &amp; Zhang
</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis id="87FF8D49ED0AFF88FB8EF8C8FBECF83E" bold="true" box="[1053,1134,1918,1942]" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="9CCC3032ED0AFF88FB8EF8C8FBECF83E" box="[1053,1134,1918,1942]" pageId="24" pageNumber="175" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
